author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Online Clothing Store
details: Create a web app for selling clothes online. Features include product catalog, user accounts, shopping cart, and secure payment gateways. Technologies: React, Node.js, MongoDB.

author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Artisan Marketplace
details: Develop a platform for artisans to showcase and sell handmade products. Includes user profiles, product listings, reviews, and messaging. Tech stack: Django, PostgreSQL, Vue.js.

author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Digital Bookstore
details: Build a website to sell digital books. Features include book categories, user authentication, search functionality, and downloadable content. Stack: Angular, Express, MongoDB.

author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Food Delivery Service
details: Create an app for ordering food online. Features include restaurant listings, menu browsing, user reviews, order tracking, and payment integration. Tools: React Native, Firebase.

author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Custom Gift Shop
details: Develop an e-commerce site for personalized gifts. Includes product customization, order tracking, wishlist, and secure checkout. Frameworks: Laravel, MySQL, React.

author: Alejandro Escamilla
title: Electronic Gadgets Store
details: Design a platform for selling electronic devices. Features include product comparisons, user reviews, order history, and integration with shipping services. Stack: ASP.NET Core, SQL Server, React.
